<title id="_5d693233-1d99-6bdb-b116-06b41638f3e7">CIPM recommended values</title>
<dl id="_e719e400-0f35-8a90-eb65-5a6f0a6d0aee"><dt>The values</dt>
<dd id="_89ca5433-faa4-01fc-ec18-c14cb82a101d"><p id="_e2fbe04e-9ca7-e6fb-ee7f-e02508597169"><stem block="false" type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
  <mstyle displaystyle="false">
